{"product_id":"hej-organic-the-protector-spf30-face-cream","title":"HEJ Organic The Protector SPF30 Face Cream 30ml","description":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eProtects your skin every day and in all weathers with SPF30 and thus counteract premature skin aging. Mineral UV filter protects you from UVA and UVB rays without any whitening. The Protector Face Cream's quickly absorbed texture is light and moisturizing.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003eLight day care with SPF30 for all skin types\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003eMineral UV filter absorbs quickly without whitening\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003eVitamin C and hyaluronic acid protect the skin and moisturize\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003eNow even more sustainable: Aluminum tube (100% recyclable) for complete emptying of the product\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e100% vegan and natural\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eApply me to your face, neck and décolleté in the morning, as well as every now and then if you spend a long time outdoors.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e Aqua, Opuntia Ficus-Indica Flower Extract*, Caprylic\/Capric Triglyceride, Titanium Dioxide, Glycine Soja Oil*, Glyceryl Citrate\/Lactate\/Linoleate\/Oleate, Butyrospermum Parkii Butter*, Zinc Oxide, Prunus Amygdalus Dulcis Oil*, Pongamia Glabra Seed Oil*, Glycerin, Opuntia Ficus-Indica Seed Oil*, Sodium Hyaluronate, Simmondsia Chinensis Seed Oil*, Citrus Paradisi Fruit Extract*, Tocopherol, Polyglyceryl-2 Dipolyhydroxystearate, Polyglyceryl-3 Diisostearate, Sodium PCA, Sorbitol, Ascorbyl Palmitate, Hydrogenated Coco-Glycerides, Acacia Senegal Gum, Alumina, Lauroyl Lysine, Xanthan Gum, Levulinic Acid, Cetearyl Alcohol, p-Anisic Acid, Glyceryl Caprylate, Stearic Acid, Glyceryl Stearate Citrate, Glyceryl Stearate, Parfum**, Citral**, Citronellol*, Limonene*, Linalool** \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e*ingredients from certified organic agriculture\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e**natural essential oils\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Hej","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":50905809551687,"sku":null,"price":14.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":false}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/hej-organic-the-protector-spf30-face-cream-30ml-965181.png?v=1739897165","url":"https:\/\/bioskina.com\/products\/hej-organic-the-protector-spf30-face-cream","provider":"bioskina","version":"1.0","type":"link"}